  "text": "Observations of daily living is a vernacular introduced by researchers involved in Project HealthDesign, a US program of Robert Wood Johnson Foundation focused on innovation in Ppersonal Health Records [CITATION_1] . ODLs were \"encountered\" in the making of the project and are defined as a type of patient-defined and patient-generated data.",
